281
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:35,800
I’ll come back for it tonight. Bye-bye.

282
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:37,440
- Wait…
- I’ll be back tonight.

283
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:38,800
Take it with you first.

284
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:39,920
Hey.

285
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:45,440
Move a little.

286
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,320
