287
00:27:51,320 --> 00:27:53,200
So pretty.

288
00:27:53,240 --> 00:27:55,720
- Freshie, look this way.
- Freshie, over here.

289
00:27:55,760 --> 00:27:58,320
- Freshie!
- Take photos, take photos.

290
00:27:58,320 --> 00:28:00,600
- So pretty.
- So pretty.

291
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:02,240
