293
00:28:08,040 --> 00:28:09,040
Sound okay?

294
00:28:10,040 --> 00:28:12,000
You’re new, right?

295
00:28:12,040 --> 00:28:13,520
My name is Wanneung.

296
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:18,080
Okay, I’ll have you take care of May,

297
00:28:18,120 --> 00:28:20,680
