- Khun Waanwaan.

302
00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:30,800
- How are you?
- I’m good.

303
00:28:30,800 --> 00:28:32,440
- You look so handsome today.
- That’s P’ Waanwaan.

304
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:34,400
