311
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:51,800
Okay.

312
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:54,120
And don’t forget to tell May about the reporters.

313
00:28:54,840 --> 00:28:56,240
- Got it.
- Go.

314
00:28:57,920 --> 00:29:00,040
Smile nicely, sweetheart. Smile.

315
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:04,480
