319
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:12,640
what do they mean?

320
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:21,720
Hey.

321
00:29:21,920 --> 00:29:24,320
What are you doing lurking around there?

322
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:29,080
I just came to tell May that

323
00:29:29,120 --> 00:29:31,000
