324
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:34,000
And there will be reporters waiting
to interview her after the event.

325
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:35,440
Are you okay, May?

326
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:40,440
I’m fine.

327
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:45,440
The stage is ready.
Are you ready, May?

328
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:51,720
May, is your leg okay?

329
00:29:52,120 --> 00:29:53,400
It’s okay now.

330
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:56,400
