331
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:58,120
I can walk much better now.

332
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:22,680
So beautiful.

333
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:25,000
- Perfect.
- So good.

334
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:27,880
- So pretty.
- The aura is unreal.

335
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:31,880
- You’re glowing, sweetheart.
- Your aura is shining. So beautiful.

336
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:34,200
- May, look at this camera.
- You look amazing on camera.

337
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:37,320
- Such strong aura. Beautiful.
- Totally glowing. So beautiful.

338
00:30:37,600 --> 00:30:38,880
Flawless head to toe.

339
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:40,200
- Beautiful.
- So beautiful.

340
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:42,040
Miss May, are you ready?

341
00:30:42,080 --> 00:30:44,440
- I’m ready.
- Okay, let’s start.

342
00:30:44,520 --> 00:30:46,600
- I want to ask…
- Wait, wait.

343
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,880
