344
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,600
Please step aside,
you’re in the frame.

345
00:30:49,640 --> 00:30:51,400
- Let me do the interview first.
- Move a bit, dear.

346
00:30:51,440 --> 00:30:53,480
- She’s being interviewed.
- Please, dear…

347
00:30:53,520 --> 00:30:55,440
- Ready.
- Thank you.

348
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:58,880
About the leaked photos last night,
what happened?

349
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:01,080
So does this mean May
has broken up with her husband…

350
00:31:01,120 --> 00:31:03,200
