352
00:31:04,840 --> 00:31:06,200
What do you mean…

353
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,880
- What do you mean?
- Is it true?

354
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:10,880
How about we talk about today’s event first?

355
00:31:12,320 --> 00:31:14,400
- Okay.
- Okay.

356
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:17,480
First of all, I really want to thank
the executives

357
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:20,080
for giving me the opportunity
to be a presenter, and

358
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:22,160
I hope everyone will support

359
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:24,920
this great product from the brand as well.

360
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:27,120
- She’s so good at selling.
- So cute, such a pro.

361
00:31:27,120 --> 00:31:29,640
- Customers will love her.
- Sales are going to be huge.

362
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:31,480
As for Win…

363
00:31:31,520 --> 00:31:33,600
- So how is it?
- Go on, dear.

364
00:31:33,640 --> 00:31:35,600
I want to confirm that

365
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:38,040
