366
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:40,280
- Really just friends?
- Friends?

367
00:31:40,320 --> 00:31:41,320
Just friends.

368
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:43,920
But about Win coming back to Thailand…

369
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:45,800
I think Win might

370
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:48,120
