371
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:50,800
- What? Good news?
- Hold on, wait…

372
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,800
What kind of good news?
Is he getting married?

373
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:55,280
Or are you two getting back together?

374
00:31:55,320 --> 00:31:56,880
Which is it?

375
00:31:56,920 --> 00:31:58,400
I meant work-related news.

376
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:01,040
- Oh.
- Oh.

377
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:03,200
As in work…

378
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:05,880
Win might be working on
a really big project.

379
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:08,840
Like an international co-production film.

380
00:32:11,040 --> 00:32:13,120
- Did May just spoil something?
- What is she even saying?

381
00:32:13,320 --> 00:32:15,440
- Not at all.
- Not at all.

382
00:32:22,600 --> 00:32:24,240
What was May talking about?

383
00:32:24,320 --> 00:32:26,440
Is Win coming back for a co-production film?

384
00:32:26,520 --> 00:32:29,040
That’s crazy. No way.

385
00:32:29,520 --> 00:32:32,280
Is it the same project
P’ Waanwaan said Gam might get?

386
00:32:32,320 --> 00:32:33,520
That’s the one.

387
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:42,280
Excuse me.
Sorry…may I have May for a moment?

388
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:44,720
May, please come this way.

389
00:32:48,320 --> 00:32:52,600
Can we get a quick interview?
How did you two meet in that leaked photo?

390
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:55,480
- Just a quick one, please.
- P’ Waanwaan…

391
00:32:55,520 --> 00:32:57,200
- They’re definitely dating.
- Exactly.

392
00:32:57,240 --> 00:32:58,720
Sorry.

393
00:32:58,760 --> 00:33:01,520
Sorry, sorry.

394
00:33:02,320 --> 00:33:04,400
Sorry.

395
00:33:04,800 --> 00:33:06,120
P’ Waanwaan.

396
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:10,320
Are you heading out already?

397
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:12,480
- Waanwaan…
- About what just happened…

398
00:33:12,520 --> 00:33:14,200
I wasn’t trying to listen or anything,

399
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:16,000
I just happened to hear May say it.

400
00:33:16,040 --> 00:33:17,600
I’m not sure if May

401
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:19,720
said it to stir up some buzz or not,

402
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:21,960
because right now,

403
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:24,120
there’s only one co-production film,
isn’t there?

404
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:27,680
And Waanwaan has had the chance

405
00:33:27,720 --> 00:33:30,520
to talk with the investor group.

406
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:32,680
- Who?
- The project where Gam

407
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:36,040
would be taking the lead role.

408
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:37,960
- Let’s take photos of Gam.
- Photos, please.

409
00:33:37,960 --> 00:33:40,800
This is Gam,
Waanwaan’s newest girl.

410
00:33:40,840 --> 00:33:43,720
Why don’t we have Gam introduce herself
to everyone, okay?

411
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:46,480
- Hello, everyone.
- So cute.

412
00:33:46,520 --> 00:33:49,000
My name is Gam.
I’m new to the industry.

413
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:52,400
- Please take good care of me.
- Of course.

414
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:55,280
- So cute, you’re going to be huge.
- Such a sweet smile. Adorable.

415
00:33:55,320 --> 00:33:56,480
P’ Waanwaan, P’ Waanwaan.

416
00:33:56,520 --> 00:34:00,520
So does that mean you’ll be returning
as Win Pawee’s personal manager?

417
00:34:00,520 --> 00:34:01,520
Yeah, that’s the question.

418
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:03,480
A question like that…

419
00:34:03,520 --> 00:34:05,720
