423
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:14,680
But once we talk and have an update…

424
00:34:14,720 --> 00:34:16,840
Please let us know as soon as you can.

425
00:34:17,240 --> 00:34:19,320
Let’s bring them out together.

426
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,440
Sure.

427
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,480
Go, go, go.

428
00:34:23,520 --> 00:34:25,280
- How is it? Nervous?
- A little.

429
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:27,480
- Don’t be scared. Smile and be confident.
- Hello, P’ Waanwaan.

430
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:29,400
- My name is Wanneung.
- You can start the interview.

431
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:32,520
- The flash always catches us, you know?
- P’ Waanwaan.

432
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:33,920
Yes?

433
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:37,400
My name is Wanneung, P’ Waanwaan.

434
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:41,440
- P’ Waanwaan, I’m going to the restroom for a bit.
- Okay.

435
00:34:45,120 --> 00:34:47,040
- P’ Waanwaan.
- I’ll go with you.

436
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,920
P’ Waanwaan.

437
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,120
Wanneung.

438
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:52,720
Are you done already?

439
00:34:53,240 --> 00:34:55,840
It’s not done yet. Hurry up and help clear things first.

440
00:35:26,600 --> 00:35:28,240
Are you trying to kick me out?

441
00:35:29,120 --> 00:35:31,000
I’m not leaving.

442
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:37,480
You…don’t let go of me.

443
00:36:37,520 --> 00:36:39,400
Please help me.

444
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,680
You broke into someone else’s house.

445
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:42,080
Why should I help you?

446
00:36:42,120 --> 00:36:43,120
You…

447
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:49,600
- Please…
- Get out of my house.

448
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:50,840
No.

449
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:53,000
You…

450
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:56,000
I’m not leaving.

451
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:58,240
Go.

452
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:01,600
Please let me stay here.

453
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:03,480
Please have mercy on me.

454
00:37:03,520 --> 00:37:05,680
Please, feel sorry for me.

455
00:37:05,720 --> 00:37:07,320
Don’t kick me out.

456
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:44,000
Hey, that was my first kiss.

457
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:45,800
What are you doing, Win Pawee?

458
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,080
You have to take responsibility.

459
00:37:47,120 --> 00:37:48,920
You…hey…

460
00:37:49,040 --> 00:37:50,920
You’re the one who kissed me.

461
00:37:54,120 --> 00:37:56,200
It was an accident.

462
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:59,000
But still, you have to take responsibility.

463
00:37:59,040 --> 00:38:01,320
Because yesterday you already saw me…

464
00:38:01,720 --> 00:38:02,880
naked once.

465
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:04,640
And today you’re still going to steal…

466
00:38:06,040 --> 00:38:08,600
my first kiss too.

467
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:10,080
Even if I’m crazy about celebrities,

468
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:11,840
