- That doesn’t even count as a kiss.

473
00:38:22,520 --> 00:38:24,040
If you’re gonna kiss…

474
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:28,240
Hey! Hey!

475
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:29,280
You! You!

476
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:30,800
- What are you doing to me?
- Kissing.

477
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:32,600
Stop it! Stop!

478
00:38:32,640 --> 00:38:33,640
Stop!

479
00:38:33,640 --> 00:38:35,040
Or I’ll…

480
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:37,000
- You’ll what?
- I’ll…

481
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:38,640
What exactly?

482
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:41,320
I’ll…

483
00:38:43,520 --> 00:38:44,800
I’ll tell the press.

484
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,840
I’ll expose everything.

485
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:49,320
And most importantly…

486
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,800
I’ll tell May too.

487
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:53,320
That you’re here.

488
00:39:00,040 --> 00:39:02,240
Maybe I should call the press now.

489
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:07,120
Who should I call...

490
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:09,880
One Day Entertainment News?

491
00:39:09,920 --> 00:39:11,480
What’s the number again...

492
00:39:11,520 --> 00:39:12,520
Wait.

493
00:39:14,640 --> 00:39:17,040
So, have you decided?

494
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:21,200
Why don’t you tell me your story?

495
00:39:21,200 --> 00:39:22,800
In detail.

496
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:25,920
Convince me you’re not
a scammer or a sasaeng.

497
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:28,400
In detail, right?

498
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,440
Yeah.

499
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:32,600
I was born on May sixth, okay?

500
00:39:32,640 --> 00:39:35,200
- That’s too detailed.
- Then what do you want from me?

501
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:38,400
Start with why your mom sold the house.

502
00:39:38,440 --> 00:39:40,960
Why you ditched the ticket 
and didn’t go to England.

503
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:46,920
Well…

504
00:39:47,040 --> 00:39:48,320
It’s just that…

505
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:50,280
I have a dream.

506
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:53,000
I want to be a superstar, just like you.

507
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:54,400
So…

508
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,800
Ever since I was a kid,

509
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:57,400
I’ve been going to auditions,

510
00:39:57,440 --> 00:39:59,600
and performing in stage plays.

511
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:00,800
Right now,

512
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:02,280
I’m an extra,

513
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:04,200
and part of the backstage crew,

514
00:40:04,200 --> 00:40:06,320
