515
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:08,440
to stay in the entertainment industry.

516
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:11,480
That’s my life.

517
00:40:11,520 --> 00:40:13,000
Detailed enough for you?

518
00:40:13,040 --> 00:40:15,240
Anything else you want to hear?

519
00:40:20,120 --> 00:40:21,400
Hey…you.

520
00:40:21,640 --> 00:40:23,720
Did you just fall asleep on me?

521
00:40:24,520 --> 00:40:26,840
Hey, were you even listening?

522
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:28,680
I talked for so long.

523
00:40:28,720 --> 00:40:30,080
